# Block search indexing on customer-facing intake forms
/meta-intake.html
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow, noarchive

/meta-intake
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow, noarchive

/amazon-intake.html
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow, noarchive

/amazon-intake
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow, noarchive

# R2-backed evidence files are private-by-obscurity + served only via signed Function
/files/*
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow, noarchive
  Cache-Control: private, max-age=86400
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
